      <text>8.3.11 (Which geo series have a sum?)</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>Complete the following table by finding the common ratio of each geometric series, and determining whether the sum to infinity exists. If it does exist, give the value in the final column; if not, then enter <code>none</code>.</p><table style="text-align: center; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;" cellpadding="10" border="1" bordercolor="#3a87ad">
